author: Samuel Osborne
title: London terror attack: Bomb squad called to Parliament after suspicious package found in vehicle
text:
17 GMT Click to followThe Independent Online 
A bomb squad has been called to investigate a suspicious vehicle near Parliament after a suspected terror attack . 
An announcement made in parliament said the discovery had halted a planned evacuation. 
More follows
